item.title: EP 89 - YouTube Shutdown: Proof Of Reptilians?
item.itunes:title: YouTube Shutdown: Proof Of Reptilians?
item.description:
Today we try to figure out what’s real and what’s not, then we discuss the conspiracy theories that have already popped up regarding the Youtube shutdown.

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

“Deep Fakes” is a slang term for an AI program that can take the actions on one screen and project them onto another. So, with the right amount of images and a hell of a lot of computing power, I could win the Super Bowl. But could this tech be used for more nefarious purposes?

Then we spend 15 minutes talking about Youtube being shut down for an hour. Did a video get uploaded that was so dangerous the whole site had to go down? Was it reptilians? Politicians eating kids? A warning of an incoming disaster? None of the above?
